def transform(sequence):
    part1, part2 = sequence[:5], sequence[5:]
    part1 = [int(i) for i in part1]
    zeros = part1.count(0)
    non_zeros = 5 - zeros
    final_sequence = [0]*zeros + [non_zeros]*non_zeros + [int(i) for i in part2]
    return "".join(map(str, final_sequence))
